TSHWANE University of Technology students gathered to mourn the death of Katlego Monareng during a memorial service at the Soshanguve campus on Thursday. Monareng was shot dead during the Student Representative Council (SRC) elections at the Soshanguve campus last week. The Independent Police Investigative Directorate (IPID) is investigating whether Monareng was killed by the cops as widely believed by the students. Photos by Morapedi Mashashe  On Wednesday, the daring Soshanguve TUT students burned tyres and any flammable objects on the busiest street  in Pretoria as they demanded justice for Katlego. Photos by Morapedi Mashashe 